Interface DefinitionNodeKey

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    IsaKey, NeverGroupedKey, NonZeroGroupKey, RoleInclusionKey, UnionGroupKey, ZeroGroupKey

    public interface DefinitionNodeKey
    Interface for definition node keys that can provide class expressions and axioms to a concept definition.

    • Method Detail

      • collect

        void collect(org.semanticweb.owlapi.model.OWLDataFactory df,
             org.semanticweb.owlapi.util.DefaultPrefixManager prefixManager,
             List<org.semanticweb.owlapi.model.OWLAxiom> axioms,
             Set<org.semanticweb.owlapi.model.OWLClassExpression> terms,
             DefinitionNode definitionNode)
        Adds terms to an OWL object intersection which will be part of a concept definition. If the class expressions needs to be described using equivalence axioms, adds those axioms to the set of collected axioms as well.
        Parameters:
        df - the OWLDataFactory to use for creating OWL objects
        prefixManager - the DefaultPrefixManager for retrieving fully qualified OWL object identifiers
        axioms - the axioms under collection (out parameter)
        terms - the concept definition terms under collection (out parameter)
        definitionNode - the definition node to process
